{
  "stem": "7455.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Perhaps people whose home was not destroyed will have more, who are better in a position to be active now.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I'm physically destroyed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they picked the eldest and prominent people of the town, that they should be in charge, that they could represent the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not know anything because we were sitting on our premises.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were activities going on in town already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we waited for the bedding to dry up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We should be able to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the sun was out, and after the whole day turning, we were able to go in, move back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was damp, but we had to have a shelter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we knew that we have no roof, that when it rains, it comes down to us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my father got busy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to get new straw because the straw was wet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He went-- they went to the farms and got more, fresh bundles of straw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the sun was hot, so the sheets and everything was dry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And some things were left still outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Just the necessity-- necessities, we should be able to move in again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then my father said, it's important to fix the roof.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They climbed up on the roof and started removing the metal sheets and put it on a pitch, which created like an attic.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They-- with poles, he supported.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the, the, the fl-- which was the floor, this our ceiling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Those steel beams were strong, so he could walk on it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was safe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Besides, it was with rubble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So my father made-- covered the cellar like in a pitch, like a tent, and supported it with beams, and put all those metal sheets on it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So if the water comes, it's going to roll off.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
